  "instructions": [
    "Heat ghee in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add onion, garlic, carrot, and celery. Cook until the vegetables are softened.",
    "Add lamb and cook until browned on all sides.",
    "Add lamb broth, rice, salt, and pepper. Bring to a boil, then reduce heat to low.",
    "Simmer, covered, for 20 minutes.",
    "Stir in sriracha and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh herbs if desired.",
    "Let the harees rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Divide the harees among 4-6 bento boxes or individual serving dishes.",
    "Cover and refrigerate for at least 30 minutes or until chilled."
